javac.file

类 RelativePath

  • java.lang.Object
    • javac.file.RelativePath
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Comparable<RelativePath>
    直接已知子类:
    RelativePath.RelativeDirectory, RelativePath.RelativeFile

    public abstract class RelativePath
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<RelativePath>
    Used to represent a platform-neutral path within a platform-specific container, such as a directory or zip file. Internally, the file separator is always '/'.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.
